15 April 2003All media are invited to a briefing in preparation for the Parliamentary address by President Thabo Mbeki on the Truth and Reconciliation Commission recommendations. The briefing will be addressed by the Chief Executive Officer of the GCIS, Mr. Joel Netshitenzhe and the Director-General in the Presidency Reverend Frank Chikane.Details are as follows:Venue: Good Hope Auditorium, Tuynhuys, Parliament, Cape Town Date: 15 April 2003. Time: 12h30 - 13h30 (12:30 - 1:30 pm)Enquiries Sputnik Ratau Tel: 021 461 6827/0058Colin Cruywagen Cell: 082 377 9916Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)